  "instructions": [
    "Preheat oven to 400°F (200°C).",
    "Toss diced sweet potato with 1 tbsp olive oil, salt, pepper, ginger, garlic, and maple syrup until coated.",
    "Spread sweet potato on a baking sheet and roast for 20 minutes, flipping halfway.",
    "While sweet potato roasts, combine callaloo, sauerkraut, lemon juice, salt, pepper, and remaining olive oil in a bowl.",
    "Massage the leafy mixture for 2 minutes to wilt and release juices.",
    "After sweet potato is crisp, remove from oven and let cool slightly.",
    "Add roasted sweet potato to the salad and toss gently.",
    "Sprinkle roasted almonds and chopped cilantro over the salad.",
    "Taste and adjust seasoning with more lemon or salt if needed.",
    "Serve immediately, optionally with a glass of water infused with lemon slices."
  ],
